{"h2cd06b1eg54e8g484bgae4dg12b5759315f5": ["Don't go botherin' my pigeon! He's <i>mine.</i>", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "3adc95a0-ddb6-0493-d2ec-283b2c57f321"], "hdf5f030egf51dg4aafg9085g055ee01c7f59": ["So I see. Do you have plans for this 'pigeon'?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "a8996d22-0bc1-07c7-a657-37250969add9"], "hf312eff8g8b28g4c26ga21fgf459a22e9bf9": ["Keep him safe. Listen to him coo. Till I gets hungry or some such.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "6e34da8e-a3c1-81d8-f852-1ee9ca992a0f"], "h5c2d2534g13e0g4706g8d75gf9bdf8559e37": ["What's it to ya?", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "0f51503f-1d91-85ca-f9a4-b9890c7560fb"], "h1781a264g3260g4ba9g8edcg4d7732c88119": ["Your pet is actually a rather famous writer.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "994d95aa-b4c9-a837-38e9-75d9460e4ffa"], "habe07e92g7bbdg4788gb8a2ga9a5aaea16fa": ["<i>Him?</i>", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "9b86593c-cd8f-ab2e-c957-a58caaa3b209"], "ha4da3468gb16ag4cc8ga2e7gb29cd359cccb": ["Nahhh.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "08fceeaa-6ba9-f70d-668c-d5ac14cb2cce"], "he714e589g5f55g452bga87bg7383da05446c": ["I was admiring him. I'd like one of my own.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "ac640f04-b0f1-572f-5f6a-f1f780c138bd"], "ha7a9618fg7137g4b41g9d63gb4be53d11ecb": ["Then <i>catch</i> one on your own.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "adaeb484-d609-1150-e6e7-1ff831591df6"], "h40aa74c3g3379g4760gb71fg1d35c1540027": ["*The mark glows, but you feel nothing in response. Your illithid power is beyond reach until you rest.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "e68b9bc6-afc0-07e1-f254-75beac880235"], "hc560dc1fg02f3g4868g8853g9a388cc47f59": ["Withholding prisoners? Your boss won't be happy to hear that.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "7cdbad65-2040-f660-af88-0bbb861cbf15"], "h537a0385g465bg4d9eg9a3dg158aa4af8a18": ["What?! I... I ain't. Minthara don't give a cake what <i>you </i>think.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "8bf62702-88ef-1294-9749-f03949130439"], "hb6591b17ge5cbg4bcagaaedg4889dc730670": ["Bah. Just take him, if you care so much. See if he'll sing for the likes of <i>you </i>though. Bloody fink.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "b6e766ea-0706-711b-f900-7b5eba3af8f5"], "h8dae9b4ag2818g4725g9571g720ab2a05023": ["I've taken a shine to this one. How much do you want for him?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "a5ff24b5-cbe9-09ce-4b24-590378b06aa1"], "h36048615g5853g4ddcgb447gbf010349d946": ["More'n you've got, mate. I likes him.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "61bd7946-36c0-b3cb-fcaf-f3b9c891d04b"], "h127f1fa5g5d11g4ef2g8857g12b9927f9f1d": ["But, erm, how much <i>do </i>ya got?", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "063807a2-e6ad-293f-4dd7-4dc03c1878db"], "h2f23a70bg84e0g4847gb85fg1dafad6379ef": ["<i>Offer a small fortune. </i>([GEN_CheckMagicPocketGold_4_5dac5eea-faeb-459c-b675-46c51519b784])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "162b9f6d-244e-229e-56d6-5b1751b7f7ae"], "h58a48131g35c8g4402gba9egf4e58e34284d": ["Eh! I could buy a bagoolion pigeons with that much!", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "b2719d4a-828a-b340-859c-34c2ffbac46f"], "h961ac9a5g6294g4a17gbe4bg8c2586a79068": ["Please. You ain't got that much. Look at that state of you.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "55004532-b301-5148-5fe1-3edcff218f31"], "h7dadf5e3g8267g4d56gba79gdb7974d182ec": ["<i>Offer a lord's ransom. </i>([GEN_CheckMagicPocketGold_3_01f129ea-b4dc-44b6-8154-9a948f876a82])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "c92ef49f-5b6a-162b-9535-a037362405bc"], "hd2944c31gf566g452bg9dbdg67e686873ff6": ["Eh! I could buy twelve pigeons with that much!", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "57d68ab6-9317-8e70-06c9-b5b6c3730170"], "h6a552c37g13efg4af0ga15eg329f3cd10a44": ["Please. You ain't got that much. Look at that state of you.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "ab8334fb-e5d8-8213-22df-de59faa83d5e"], "h5652d0edg0722g4f20g8386g307aad110b01": ["<i>Offer a modest sum. </i>([GEN_CheckMagicPocketGold_2_463b0f43-5410-412d-aba3-875cf81c38ca])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "359ffb0a-e6c0-300e-d448-60619f976585"], "hd1f25edeg4b6eg4186g9583gf394aa999a86": ["Pigeon's worth more'n that times a bagoolion.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "cef4b0e2-c0cb-f6b0-cb4d-d1088b10958f"], "hb9457ed8gdf4ag4e11g8ec0g570362da321e": ["<i>Offer as little as you can spare. </i>([GEN_CheckMagicPocketGold_6057ad05-9492-4630-9f0a-be548b134c54])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "bfce1c9e-9297-21c5-62cf-fc99e97b68bc"], "hd73b61e2g49a4g477fg9ebcg345ba910cfe3": ["You funnin'? Pigeon don't take a <i>kra-kra </i>for that much.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "ed3e4a9f-1625-16a4-6f3c-c42f8049ff8b"], "hfe92b465g78bag4920g8c8fgeb55e54e762b": ["<i>Offer a bulging bag of fake gold.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "a3785423-9a4f-6fbd-1fcd-08b34e53d6ab"], "h22d5e46cg7e29g4747gaaebg3160370fc402": ["Eh! I could buy a bagoolion pigeons with that much!", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "d10a4978-b6aa-27c8-1183-49d13b8eceed"], "h7dc821afgdfb1g4ed4g88d9g8b64fda07adf": ["<i>Actually, I have no coin to spare.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "e4ad5441-2a55-362b-fb53-b59d38b08556"], "h0375dc86g7eb5g4302g9f76g766e67a327e0": ["See? You couldn't take care of him proper anyway.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "c684c1d3-8bdf-0ab4-27c3-84f4fa5fdab1"], "h647dec31ga9e9g4527gb10fg3358ed8c8a42": ["He looks weak. Sick, even. He won't last long in there.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "6cca8a7e-7a00-33c5-4afc-260c02806745"], "haaa26755g310fg4cb6g8c42gb72ace738d4a": ["Take him for a jog, why don't ya. And don't let the lads snatch him up. No tellin' what they'll do to him.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "e5c3553b-0670-8b71-ea25-53ab0cea8445"], "h8fa715f2g3a0bg4c17g8143gd6479bf5ccf3": ["Bring him back when he's all tuckered out.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "01364917-dd16-d548-d4f8-7d3b75f17a74"], "h9eacb3f3gf233g4c0fgb9ecgb6567ad5a2af": ["Oh well.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "c531ab36-57ee-a26d-b644-7bbf99fc0906"], "h18839495gb24dg4e85g9730g6d91f6a06443": ["I'm done talking. Open the cage or you'll be sorry.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "0f19a756-e906-c5f7-6398-da099df3c70d"], "h150fedd6gf41ag4c3agb5bag9640435cb5d4": ["All right, all right, calm down. I don't wants no trouble.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "4e47d1ce-e8b0-fdc5-a2fd-a9845d23d05c"], "he39648fegdb2ag4b5fg8a8eg8acc02d5f76d": ["Sorry for what? Stupid <i>ranga.</i>", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "8c423cc8-3ca9-8a41-9e69-38df4038a6a2"], "h79353119g301eg4497g9595g0d0de936f9c4": ["<i>Read her thoughts.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "effc7f5c-929d-fe24-0229-6626d4dabdf2"], "h3fb146cdgd5fcg460cga8dbgb3a44b464965": ["<i>This </i>ranga <i>better not go yappin' 'bout my pigeon. I shoulda turned him over to Minthara by now, but he's such a nice little pigeon.</i>", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "c95358bf-6b62-442c-d304-34d72c2fc5da"], "h946b9d48g7b08g4c1cgb370gf0e42a49425e": ["OI! STOP THAT!", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "23213fc6-b1e8-2a23-ec54-d64e8b24689e"], "hc8e96247g853dg44b5gb793g7a29436111c3": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "a867bb0c-93d2-4fef-d661-cebc0bcb4176"], "h25b72261g7b08g40b7gb6d4g12fb831a6869": ["*A strange symbol glows, marked on their flesh, and something within you stirs in response.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "f2c2c865-4a7d-d77a-5126-d991ddb9aa89"], "h445457a7g8598g4ccagb7d4gf5a0eda6db12": ["Set him free.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "323b0355-5b2a-490f-a30f-ba28a712a92a"], "h26279268gc6d7g4fdag96cfgef68ef913368": ["Y-yes, of course - I didn't realise who you was.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "f96883eb-565a-641a-de39-0c65b7725285"], "h01cc357ag6c87g42ffgb408gd44d9a5deb11": ["*A shiver runs across your mind... you feel sated.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "fc8afa88-3174-cff9-fb11-f479ec288eed"], "h29616694g327eg4091g9fe5gafac7b3a76d9": ["Here's the key. Pigeon's all yours.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "f89a33fb-54a5-33f7-6ba6-24938b0a8002"], "h153a370fgb235g48b8g8480g1e5877631e45": ["Huh?! It were right in my pocket... someone musta nicked it! Bloody maggots.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "a853a77a-f2e6-0d84-1cb7-6a9a1d0f24c0"], "he5685c9eg4a53g45d9g8a4eg78ac9c8d667c": ["Here's the key. Pigeon's all yours.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "4642b47a-cf8b-432b-1f9c-cd0a3328c811"], "hd1bc504ag0e5cg40f9g9be7g09743ec09d5e": ["*Something stirs deep within you, hungry and alert... it's taking something you'll never get back.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "9f5db565-8c8d-921f-096d-7cbef0eb0ade"], "hfe0a70b2g2a48g4703gbc2cg24da4035428c": ["*Your mind lurches, reeling suddenly as if... bitten.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "93892dcc-7578-0dd4-0435-6d4d80a90d24"], "hc89f627bgb3f2g4ecega897g82acc1f3d4a9": ["*A shadow swims across your vision, and a familiar voice tells you to be calm. You are loved.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "ede723c5-964e-7dc9-0b21-c67b4fa0a545"], "h31e1870bg4526g442cg93d4gc5d5c311db3c": ["*Your blood runs quicker, feeding the gnawing absence at the centre of your mind.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "d9a7f089-8d41-65f0-8d87-05ecaa81ea97"], "h6a85b6fbg1b6cg49efg9d08g3b77852602e8": ["*The presence deep in your mind is awake, unblinking. This is it. A single word pervades your consciousness: 'Soon'.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "c908041a-0a9a-f928-6ad5-6892878e130e"], "hec0c9f57g6a57g431cgb8eagbe6f63b8fe65": ["*Your mind is full, bursting with ecstasy and terror. Finally, it is coming. You are becoming.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "ecd25ae9-f19d-8299-c299-957c51735f1d"], "hb005e9d4gcac1g4536g95e1gfcd0a95a905b": ["NO.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "e87623e4-90ac-9822-4b5d-9f13cf1d86ba"], "hf93fefd1gd23fg41e7ga012gc144d03c9eff": ["Set him free.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "2cc16533-e538-8c2a-98cd-bdf26da07e84"], "h2bdaa825gdfe2g42ebgbc22g25dbc75de5f9": ["*As the symbol glows, power courses through you. <i>Authority</i>.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "141bca25-2dd0-d0aa-36bf-b451d266fe8c"], "hac8a7320g384bg4295ga128gd0d3f997580e": ["I hate to see such a lovely creature in a cage.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "c35e8bc9-417e-159e-3255-85cb01ebd395"], "h3fa9bb88gb082g4ae4ga972g872faf7ef4a2": ["Ehh, he don't mind. Keeps him safe from me mates! Raids make 'em rabid.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "c01bd793-2474-7448-af89-759caef0f80c"], "h8b295b3cgb38cg47b6g8605g5fe697b57544": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "19105703-9c60-0a9f-eadc-4f439bf92978"], "hfc6f01b6g30b9g473agb01bg62dacc594426": ["Does your bird have a name?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "0ba88579-f4ef-a55f-21a7-11f556f06544"], "h28fa3de4ga676g4ef9g8da5gc2b9268bcca6": ["Erm...<i>Pidge.</i>", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "f80fc9ae-cafe-ccb4-1ca4-abed96f9ae59"], "h5a12250bgf8f5g4ac1g9f0cg99bc9c14bf66": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "1f2d7a89-0d47-ebbd-3fb9-b74a24fd26a8"], "hc2827a40gca44g4892g95b6g75928c67965e": ["'Scuse me, True Soul Yourself.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "20c0a191-0a99-2d4c-0eb9-dcb1a2ef2223"], "h2c848587gac4eg477eg9b33ge40035afcff8": ["Git! This'n's mine.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "7283ad84-f6ba-d3f2-3c38-55fcfe930de0"], "h319c247ag2392g49b7gb326g50f34447ee73": ["Don' bother the <i>talent.</i>", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "3d0f115e-3622-1785-21af-c463c1838338"], "ha93c5654ga4f0g44f5g90d8gdb9caaee743e": ["Hope Pidge is behavin' himself.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "364861a9-af70-f202-2e5b-16f0d38914f4"], "h7a81167fg99f7g4f90ga127g0be08edf40bf": ["Where'd that bloody key go...", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Guard_AtCage.html", "7c156490-08f9-155d-6de9-46a3944b85ae"]}